015), Deguen (2012) and\nLasbleis and Deguen (2015) on the dynamics of the inner core, and to Rubie et\nal. (2015) on core formation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 24 May 2019 19:19:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-28"}
