ven by material constants),\nthe stress drop is very sharp due to transition of solutions in a snap-back\nbifurcation. These features show good agreement with experimental observations\nand shed light on the difficulties of numerical simulations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 24 May 2019 21:33:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 30 May 2019 19:08:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-03"}
